Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.56,0:00:06.27,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,It's still early in the morning\Nbut I already ate too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.69,0:00:09.53,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Let's run a bit and get back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.07,0:00:13.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.41,0:00:15.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.04,0:00:23.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good morning, you're up early.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.13,0:00:29.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not a suspicious person!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.23,0:00:46.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A lost item?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.31,0:00:48.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.66,0:00:57.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to keep it for myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.41,0:01:00.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's exactly 30 million yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.58,0:01:03.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wasn't reported lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.29,0:01:03.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.33,0:01:07.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's a good thing you're the one who found it, Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.42,0:01:11.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you're a police detective. Sorry for doubting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.30,0:01:17.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So Sasamoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, do you run this course every day?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.97,0:01:22.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. I just hope whoever lost it gets it back sometime soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.93,0:01:23.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.73,0:01:27.40,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It doesn't matter how many times you try,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.40,0:01:29.23,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}whether it's in love, cases, today, or tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.23,0:01:30.82,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}30 million yen lying in a lost bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.82,0:01:32.94,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What is its owner planning?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.94,0:01:34.61,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.61,0:01:36.40,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.40,0:01:39.37,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.33,0:03:30.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have I seen anyone carring a brown bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.87,0:03:35.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. The person who dropped it might not have been from this area though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.84,0:03:37.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll ask my neighbors as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.96,0:03:39.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.43,0:03:42.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You did it, Detective Takagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.30,0:03:43.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard you found a lot of money!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.39,0:03:47.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How do you guys know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.02,0:03:49.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We call ourselves the Detective Boys for a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.64,0:03:55.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, if the bag's owner doesn't claim it within six months, then it'll belong to you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.27,0:03:56.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll be a billionaire!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.86,0:03:59.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.70,0:04:04.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a policeman's job to return lost items.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.07,0:04:07.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh? So you won't treat me to some eel bowls?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.45,0:04:08.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Told you so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.25,0:04:12.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll help you find whoever lost it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.96,0:04:15.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We don't have school, so we have some free time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.38,0:04:18.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You found it today early in the morning, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.80,0:04:20.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, around 6 AM.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.84,0:04:25.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Today was my day off so I slept at a friend's place nearby last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.43,0:04:31.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, while I was jogging with a woman named\NSasamoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, I just ran into it right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.06,0:04:34.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the middle of the road?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.69,0:04:35.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.94,0:04:38.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a moron.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.11,0:04:40.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dropping a bag full of money...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.11,0:04:44.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's work together on this, Takagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.41,0:04:47.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If a normal citizen such as myself had found the bag...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.41,0:04:50.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.87,0:04:51.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.50,0:04:54.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? The bag's owner showed up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.29,0:04:58.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, if you need any help later, call me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.80,0:05:01.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did he come for?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.63,0:05:08.39,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Toshiyuki Hiranuma (45)\NManager of an Organic Food Shop
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.18,0:05:08.14,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Toshiyuki Hiranuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, you're the one who lost this bag, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.14,0:05:09.10,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.51,0:05:13.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His wife died from an illness recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.27,0:05:16.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The 30 million yen is from life insurance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.86,0:05:17.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.27,0:05:22.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Hiranuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, why did you drop that money?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.15,0:05:24.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it's an embarrasing story.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.36,0:05:29.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My friend was in Beika Town,\Nso I thought I'd show it to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.74,0:05:33.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you were carrying 30 million yen just to brag?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.87,0:05:38.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah. I was in such a good mood that I went for some drinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.17,0:05:42.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But when I woke up this morning, I paled when I noticed I didn't have the bag with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.46,0:05:46.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you dropped it last night, not this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.18,0:05:46.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.80,0:05:49.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.35,0:05:53.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Though since it's such a large amount, I can't exactly give it back to you right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.89,0:05:55.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.39,0:05:57.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, is this paint?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.31,0:06:02.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry? Where did I get that from?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.78,0:06:07.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, we'll call you as soon as we can give you the bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.82,0:06:11.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fine. I'm not in a hurry anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.75,0:06:17.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We found the owner right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.04,0:06:19.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Detective Boys didn't even get to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.71,0:06:21.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.09,0:06:24.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.71,0:06:27.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was just about to go to the police station.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.26,0:06:29.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're the lady from this morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.05,0:06:32.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wasn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.26,0:06:41.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I passed through there delivering newspapers at about 5 AM, and there wasn't anything there then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.31,0:06:46.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then maybe Hiranuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} dropped it later?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.04,0:06:55.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks so creepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.70,0:06:58.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you find anything, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.29,0:07:00.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.79,0:07:04.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look! Could these be Hiranuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s footprints?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.05,0:07:09.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, Hiranuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s shoes {\i1}were{\i0} dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.13,0:07:13.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And look at the paint flaking off here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.72,0:07:17.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the same as the paint on his shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.27,0:07:27.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, are you saying that\NHiranuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} came here this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.61,0:07:32.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and he put the bag here just before you arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.45,0:07:33.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Put"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.12,0:07:37.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even that early in the morning, it's hard\Nto believe that nobody'd pass here
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.66,0:07:43.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,for the entire hour that went by between\Nthe newspaper delivery guy and you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.42,0:07:45.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.59,0:07:51.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it was dropped here just before I came, then\NI should have been able to spot Hiranuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.43,0:07:52.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.26,0:08:00.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, Hiranuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} put the bag in the middle of the street with the right timing so somebody would pick it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.02,0:08:04.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was observing the situation from this warehouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.27,0:08:07.53,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A lost item?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.53,0:08:09.32,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Looks like it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.61,0:08:13.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why did he want Detective Takagi to pick it up?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.87,0:08:17.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see! It was for Sasamoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.87,0:08:24.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just happened to be here, but Sasamoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} said she jogs through this place every morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.13,0:08:28.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, he tried to make Sasamoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} pick up the 30 million yen?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.38,0:08:31.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's still very strange! It's a lot of money!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.88,0:08:32.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.30,0:08:39.72,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Hideko Sasamoto (47)\NPart-timer
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.22,0:08:38.85,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,So, we can give the bag back to its rightful owner, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.85,0:08:39.72,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.43,0:08:43.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name's Toshiyuki Hiranuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.35,0:08:45.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you know him, Sasamoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.77,0:08:49.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hiranuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}? I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.82,0:08:51.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.44,0:08:53.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who is this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.36,0:08:55.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard he's from the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.99,0:08:56.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Police?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.20,0:09:01.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She didn't look like she was lying...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.62,0:09:04.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.25,0:09:04.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.42,0:09:07.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.17,0:09:09.59,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Kunitarō Ōba (50)\NHideko's Boss
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.71,0:09:09.59,Signs,,0,0,0,,Did you find the culprit?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.84,0:09:12.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Culprit?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.22,0:09:15.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it's not the same case.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.89,0:09:22.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My name's Ōba. I'm the floor supervisor at this supermarket.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.73,0:09:25.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And so what is this case about Sasamoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s husband?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.73,0:09:30.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sasamoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s husband was murdered.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.82,0:09:38.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Last month, on the 30th, fifteen years have\Npassed and the killer still hasn't been found.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.83,0:09:41.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the statute of limitations used to be fifteen years, didn't it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.08,0:09:41.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.12,0:09:47.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hideko's quite cheerful now,\Nbut she couldn't smile at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.17,0:09:49.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was always looking down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.05,0:09:58.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, Hideko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and I are going to get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.05,0:10:03.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She refused to marry me when I asked her at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.22,0:10:08.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Out of respect for her late husband, she didn't allow herself to become happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.94,0:10:10.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that's not a good enough reason, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.57,0:10:19.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Recently, she finally started thinking about her own happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.74,0:10:27.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A few days ago, we both went to her husband's grave, to ask him to release his wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.42,0:10:32.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.67,0:10:38.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the killer shows up again, I think she'll never stop hating him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.85,0:10:41.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Supervisor!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.18,0:10:43.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry! I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.64,0:10:51.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fifteen years passed, but it's still unsolved.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.81,0:10:56.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are this case and the 30 million yen bag related?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.11,0:10:58.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.78,0:11:00.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How could they be related?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.45,0:11:02.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.83,0:11:07.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gotcha. I'm going to look into this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.25,0:11:14.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The case happened in a fourth-floor office at night at night, 15 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.13,0:11:17.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The killer didn't want to get caught on the surveillance camera,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.55,0:11:21.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so he climbed up the pipes in the gap between it and the next building up to the 4th floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.47,0:11:23.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He then sneaked into the office from the balcony.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.85,0:11:30.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He killed Akio Sasamoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, who was doing overtime by himself, and left after stealing 5 million yen in cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.98,0:11:35.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But since some footprints were left behind by the killer's tennis shoes,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.02,0:11:38.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,a list of all the people who bought these shoes was established,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.15,0:11:40.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and a thorough investigation was started.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.91,0:11:45.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hiranuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s name was also on that list.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.74,0:11:48.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see. So, that's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.41,0:11:50.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.67,0:11:57.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To redeem himself for the murder, he tried to give the 30 million yen to the widow, Sasamoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.17,0:12:05.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Once Sasamoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} had picked it up, if he didn't show himself in six months, the money would go to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.01,0:12:09.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, Hiranuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was the killer?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.56,0:12:10.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.69,0:12:13.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought the same thing at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.23,0:12:18.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Hiranuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} can't be the killer, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.55,0:12:28.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was literally impossible for him to commit the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.72,0:12:29.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.10,0:12:35.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When a police officer questioned him, he had a broken leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.85,0:12:43.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When we checked the hospital he went to, we learnt he got\Nthe plaster cast for this leg three days before the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.86,0:12:48.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He couldn't have climbed up to the 4th floor with a broken leg!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.57,0:12:51.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And he can't wear tennis shoes with a cast, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.16,0:12:52.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.54,0:12:57.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, the case from fifteen years ago and\NHiranuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s 30 million yen aren't connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.96,0:13:02.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{It was also thinking too much that he tried to make someone picking it up.}And the idea that he tried to make somebody pick it up is probably just us overthinking it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.92,0:13:03.63,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.09,0:13:07.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, a phone call! It's from Uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.68,0:13:08.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.72,0:13:10.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Uncle. What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.81,0:13:16.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle Kogorō seems to be interested in this 30 million yen case.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.85,0:13:21.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I told him what we learnt, he told me to\Nask Detective Takagi to investigate something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.48,0:13:28.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whether or not anyone Hiranuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} knew also had a broken leg at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.66,0:13:33.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s asking, I guess I can check...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.74,0:13:36.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He wondered if he could get the help of the Detective Boys, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.71,0:13:40.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said that whatever kind of information we can get is okay, as long as it's related to Hiranuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.59,0:13:43.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're assisting a Great Detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.05,0:13:47.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right! Time to investigate!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.80,0:13:50.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, see you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.05,0:13:52.55,Signs,,0,0,0,,I apologise, but the organic food shop Hiranuma is now closed.\N—Hiranuma
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.35,0:13:56.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The shop closed a month ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.35,0:14:00.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was when his sick wife died.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.98,0:14:03.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hiranuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} seems to be a very honest man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.61,0:14:06.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But something strange happened recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.49,0:14:14.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Though he said he was going for a trip for a while,\Nhe happened to come back the same day!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.03,0:14:16.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It happened a week ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.66,0:14:17.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A week ago?{\NTS: Cleaning Morita}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.87,0:14:23.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that? It was at the end of last month, on the 30th.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.17,0:14:31.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Though now I think about it, Hiranuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} said\Nsomething peculiar the previous evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.26,0:14:34.39,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You nursed your wife a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.10,0:14:38.10,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But you should relax now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.10,0:14:39.35,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Your late wife would agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.35,0:14:41.48,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I wish I could, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.40,0:14:45.65,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There was something I decided to do a long time ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.65,0:14:47.36,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But when the time came...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.36,0:14:48.44,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I got scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.44,0:14:49.40,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.86,0:14:51.70,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.82,0:14:53.53,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}really...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.37,0:14:55.99,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}such a pathetic man!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.49,0:15:02.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then he kept saying it wasn't something which could be compensated for with money.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.04,0:15:05.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, the next morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.05,0:15:09.80,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh, Hiranuma{\rHonorifics - Flashback\be10}-san{\r\be10}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.80,0:15:12.93,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You're carrying a bag. Are you going to a hot spring?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.93,0:15:15.30,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}No, I'm leaving for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.76,0:15:18.52,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Morita{\rHonorifics - Flashback\be10}-san{\r\be10}, please take care of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.89,0:15:25.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was as if he was saying his last goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.52,0:15:31.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Still, he came back the same day during the evening, saying he'd been unable to go on his trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.24,0:15:34.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.91,0:15:39.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Detective Takagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.00,0:15:40.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.58,0:15:44.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}! Already having beer at noon?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.71,0:15:46.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Today is my day off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.46,0:15:47.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.38,0:15:48.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.21,0:15:49.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One kakesoba, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.42,0:15:51.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One kakesoba, coming up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.47,0:15:58.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.76,0:16:02.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I missed a step, and then my right leg...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.23,0:16:08.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Back then, Kanzaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, you didn't have\Nyour own health insurance card, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.73,0:16:10.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.48,0:16:11.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And just what are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.32,0:16:16.66,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That day, Hiranuma{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} knew that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.70,0:16:19.41,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's why he could...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.87,0:16:28.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, what does the famous detective Kogorō Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} want with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.79,0:16:30.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know, either...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.34,0:16:33.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But first, the introductions.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.55,0:16:38.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Hideko Sasamoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}. She found the bag with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.14,0:16:42.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Takagi! Why did you call me here all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.64,0:16:43.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm busy, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.31,0:16:46.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? But you're the one who—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.19,0:16:47.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did I—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.69,0:16:51.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.44,0:16:52.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.94,0:16:54.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He fell asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.82,0:17:01.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A detective of my skill can decipher an entire case by simply listening to gossip.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.29,0:17:03.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hiranuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.83,0:17:05.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.00,0:17:10.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm here to speak about the murder-robbery you commited fifteen years ago, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.59,0:17:12.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't be serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.50,0:17:13.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.84,0:17:18.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that's impossible, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.80,0:17:22.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hiranuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} broke his leg three days prior to the murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.97,0:17:30.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just because the X-rays were tagged with Hiranuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s\Nname doesn't mean they're necessarily his!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.86,0:17:35.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean Kanzaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} borrowed his health insurance card?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.24,0:17:37.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the cast?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.03,0:17:40.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He did it himself with plaster after the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.70,0:17:41.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.62,0:17:43.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't have any proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.20,0:17:50.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Takagi, if you think Hiranuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is innocent,\Ncan you tell me why he's not objecting?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.38,0:17:56.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought about it when Kanzaki broke his leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.80,0:18:00.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My leg hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.30,0:18:02.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it's broken!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.26,0:18:04.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, at least get yourself some health insurance, you moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.27,0:18:06.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, I'll lend you mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.22,0:18:07.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Won't I be caught?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.31,0:18:10.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How could you? It doesn't even have a picture on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.06,0:18:14.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, it was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.61,0:18:15.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.40,0:18:19.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My deepest apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.53,0:18:25.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At that time I was an irresponsible coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.54,0:18:28.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A worthless delinquent.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.58,0:18:30.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.63,0:18:34.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I met a woman who changed my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.13,0:18:38.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I married her and worked honestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.05,0:18:44.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, I got my own shop, even if it was a small one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.26,0:18:51.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the happier we became, the more I regretted my past mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.31,0:18:56.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought many times about turning myself in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.24,0:19:00.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I just couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.20,0:19:03.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My wife got seriously ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.70,0:19:10.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nobody would have watched over her if I wasn't around.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.79,0:19:18.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then she died last month and I received the 30 million yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.30,0:19:23.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So then you really didn't drop it —\hyou put it there on purpose...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.80,0:19:25.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.68,0:19:28.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why did you go though all this trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.77,0:19:30.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.06,0:19:32.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you really felt guilty, you would just have to meet her and give it to her directly!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.19,0:19:35.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was a coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.73,0:19:39.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was afraid of getting caught by the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.82,0:19:41.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not right, is it, Hiranuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.61,0:19:46.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You came here a week ago, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.03,0:19:53.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You planned to give Sasamoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} the 30 million\Nyen, and then turn yourself in to the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.25,0:19:55.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you weren't able to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.92,0:20:02.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I came here, I heard them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.13,0:20:08.85,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Sasamoto{\rHonorifics - Flashback\be10}-san{\r\be10}, I proposed to Hideko{\rHonorifics - Flashback\be10}-san{\r\be10}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.93,0:20:16.86,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But she then told me that it would be too\Ndisrespectful to you if she's happy without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.56,0:20:19.40,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I understand her feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.40,0:20:21.69,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But it's been fifteen years now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.19,0:20:28.83,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Well? Could you release her from being just a victim's relative?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.53,0:20:39.67,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I won't forget you, but I want to bury that case\Nin the depths of my heart and forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.67,0:20:40.59,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.71,0:20:43.76,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.76,0:20:44.17,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.18,0:20:46.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.09,0:20:51.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since his widow was trying to forget the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.47,0:20:59.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the end, you failed to give her the\Nmoney, apologise, or turn yourself in.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.44,0:21:03.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If a killer who escaped the police\Nfor fifteen years turned himself in...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.82,0:21:06.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Reporters would've swamped the victim's relatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.49,0:21:10.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Despite her finally trying to start her new life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.00,0:21:22.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Hiranuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, no matter how much you try to convince yourself, you cannot erase the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.34,0:21:28.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But this case is special.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.59,0:21:34.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't erase it, but you {\i1}can{\i0} conclude it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.18,0:21:41.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you serve your sentence, and Sasamoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} accepts it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.19,0:21:45.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you finally put an end to it, nobody will have to bear the burden of it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.49,0:21:47.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll be able to have a fresh new start.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.95,0:21:49.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Both of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.61,0:21:50.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, Takagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.37,0:21:54.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Toshiyuki Hiranuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.24,0:21:57.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As a suspect to a robbery and a murder,\Nplease follow me to the police station.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.83,0:21:58.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.59,0:22:07.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could you accept the 30 million yen?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.76,0:22:10.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please use it yourself, when the\Ntime comes for you to start afresh.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.31,0:23:39.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.15,0:23:40.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.36,0:23:41.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.11,0:23:41.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.74,0:23:47.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, crap! I forgot about him...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.78,0:23:53.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.50,0:23:57.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.83,0:24:05.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were heading to the place of\Nsomeone who'd identify a killer for us, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.84,0:24:09.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the next Conan: The Client's Message!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.92,0:24:14.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint: Fox!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.84,0:24:16.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} got left behind?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.14,0:24:17.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Give me 10% of that 30 million yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.93,0:24:19.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He'll be fine.
